    "title": "Sara",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "sara",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Sara alikuwa mke wa Abrahamu na pia dada yake wa nusu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:29\">Mwanzo 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:12\">20:12</a>). Alisafiri na Abrahamu kutoka Uru hadi Harani na kisha hadi Kanaani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:31\">Mwanzo 11:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:5\">12:5</a>). Mara mbili, huko Misri na Gerari, Abrahamu alimwomba Sara aseme kuwa yeye ni dada yake, si mke wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10-Gen12:20\">Mwanzo 12:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:1-Gen20:18\">20:1–18</a>). Aliogopa kwamba huenda angeuawa kwa sababu yake. Licha ya ukosefu wa imani wa Abrahamu, Mungu alimlinda Sara mara zote mbili. Hii ilihifadhi ukoo ulioteuliwa ambao Mungu aliahidi kuutumia kukuza taifa la Waisraeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:2\">Mwanzo 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:19\">17:19</a>).</p><p>Sara ni mmoja wa wanawake kadhaa katika Biblia ambao walikuwa hawajapata watoto lakini kwa miujiza walipata mtoto wa kiume (tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:22-Gen30:24\">Mwanzo 30:22–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:9-1Sam1:20\">1 Samweli 1:9–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:14-2Kgs4:17\">2 Wafalme 4:14–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:5-Luke1:25\">Luka 1:5–25</a>). Baada ya Mungu kutoa ahadi kadhaa, Sara alipata mimba na kumzaa Isaka. Sara alikuwa na umri wa miaka tisini wakati hili lilipotokea, ikionyesha uwezo wa Mungu kufanya kile kinachoonekana kuwa hakiwezekani (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:17\">Mwanzo 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:5\">21:1–5</a>). Jina lake lilibadilishwa kutoka Sarai hadi Sara wakati Mungu aliahidi kuzaliwa kwa Isaka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:15-Gen17:16\">Mwanzo 17:15–16</a>). Sara anaheshimiwa kwa imani yake, ingawa alicheka utabiri wa kuzaliwa kwa Isaka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:10-Gen18:15\">Mwanzo 18:10–15</a>). Hili lilitokea miaka ishirini na tano baada ya ahadi ya kwanza ya Mungu kwa Abrahamu.</p><p>Sara alifariki akiwa na umri wa miaka 127 na alizikwa katika pango ambalo Abrahamu alinunua huko Makpela (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:1-Gen23:20\">Mwanzo 23</a>). Anajulikana kama mama wa taifa la Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:2\">Isaya 51:2</a>), kama vile Abrahamu alivyo baba yake. Anachukua nafasi muhimu katika hadithi kuhusu imani ya Abrahamu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:19\">Warumi 4:19</a>). Anawakilisha uhuru ambao Wakristo wanayo (kama watoto wa Sara, mwanamke huru) kupitia imani kwa Kristo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:21-Gal4:31\">Wagalatia 4:21–31</a>). Petro anamtumia kama mfano wa unyenyekevu mtakatifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:5-1Pet3:6\">1 Petro 3:5–6</a>). Mwandishi wa Waebrania anamwasilisha Sara kama mfano wa imani, kwa kuwa aliamini katika uwezo wa Mungu wa kutimiza ahadi zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11-Heb11:12\">Waebrania 11:11–12</a>). Maisha yake yanaonyesha kwamba Mungu ni mwaminifu, hata kama wakati wake hauendani kila mara na matarajio yetu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:29-Gen11:31\">Mwanzo 11:29–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10-Gen12:20\">12:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:15-Gen17:22\">17:15–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:9-Gen18:15\">18:9–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:1-Gen20:18\">20:1–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:13\">21:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:1-Gen23:20\">23:1–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:2\">Isaya 51:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:19\">Warumi 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:6-Rom9:9\">9:6–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:21-Gal4:31\">Wagalatia 4:21–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11-Heb11:12\">Waebrania 11:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:6\">1 Petro 3:6</a></p>",
